# Place Habbo Hotel sound effects here (.mp3, .wav, .m4a)
# Files will be converted to OGG Vorbis at build time via scripts/convert-audio-to-ogg.sh
#
# To obtain sounds:
# 1. See scripts/obtain-habbo-sounds.md for detailed instructions
# 2. Download from 101soundboards Habbo collection: https://www.101soundboards.com/boards/172347-habbo-soundboard
# 3. Or extract from Habbo v14 SWF using JPEXS Free Flash Decompiler
#
# Priority file for v1 demo: notification.mp3
